                                         DURBAN - The African National Congress (ANC) in KwaZulu-Natal is on Thursday morning appearing before the Moerane Commission of Inquiry that's investigating the underlying causes of political killings in the province. KZN ANC chair Sihle Zikalala is leading the delegation. WATCH: ANC delegation appears before Moerane inquiry 